ts on synthetic and real-world\ndatasets that different embodiments of the proposed strategy are\ncomputationally efficient and over-perform by orders of magnitude an algorithm\nbeing currently used by real-world tape file systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 21 Oct 2018 18:42:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-23"}
